{"tid":2085964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《前線手足留比香港人既口信，71見！》","createTime":"2020-06-30T06:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T06:36:02.000Z","uid":64522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"45d1117fdf855ec9288476d89f9734e9b637ccd8","tid":2085964,"uid":64522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"香港民族獨立運動Telegram消息發佈平台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hknimC/30252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhknimC%2F30252&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=43ecd48b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknimC/30252</a><br />\n<br />\n#手足投稿 #一定要睇<br />\n<br />\n《前線手足留比香港人既口信，71見！》<br />\n<br />\n其實都抗爭左成年啦！我諗大家都會明白&mdash;&mdash;光復香港<br />\n唔係淨係食黃店 repo下文宜<br />\n咁就光復到香港，而係做出黎，我哋已經再冇退路。<br />\n<br />\n我再懇請大家記得&mdash;&mdash;香港人，呢個身份真係有今生無來世。<br />\n未有反送中風波之前，我諗我真係一隻好完整既港豬<br />\n但呢次唔同，一次又一次係眼前既警暴、朋友既失蹤，下意識到好大件事，但我唔覺得自已做錯野！<br />\n捍衛自由，係我哋既目的。<br />\n<br />\n但7 1國安法就正式打到黎，<br />\n乜野分裂國家罪、判國罪，大家都會被例入黑名單；大家要面對既可能一生既。<br />\n監獄生活，什至送中<br />\n白色恐怖，已經最大化<br />\n中共既高壓打手段，加上警察既濫打、濫捕，我哋真係唔反抗咩？<br />\n但我哋都係人都會攰，為捍自由不惜一切！<br />\n<br />\n但我希望7月1見到大家出黎！<br />\n假如7月1再失敗，證明我亦會返回原來既生活，希望7月1見到你哋 ！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"9f609de5bdc7a4494aa65106bfa3c3e43cd9c2f7","tid":2085964,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45da26768c3681980034f539aa1e46a8cad7adab","tid":2085964,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"前線手足留比香港人既口信，71見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2085944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2085944</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推呢到"},{"pid":"677754296acae9a5036ee348e78de94cca76372f","tid":2085964,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:27:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a51d9ff328e0554b98759bd3cf239d3c1c68456","tid":2085964,"uid":64522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab942aa62d3f458d2908f3a233e46668fa26ad7","tid":2085964,"uid":64522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:36:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}